Description: RivRetrieve provides access to global river gauge data from a variety of national-level river agencies. The package interfaces with the national-level agency websites to provide access to river gauge locations, river discharge, and river stage. Currently, the package is available for the following countries: Australia, Brazil, Canada, Chile, France, Japan, South Africa, the United Kingdom, and the United States.
